  "title": " [산후보약/산후보약잘짓는한의원] 고운맘카드 지정 이수한의원",
  "addDate": "2014. 4. 22.",
  "categoryNo": "24",
  "parentCategoryNo": "8",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110189446985",
  "html_size": 192733,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110189446985\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110189446985\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">[산후보약/산후보약잘짓는한의원]산후보약 먹는 시기</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">아내의 출산을 앞둔 산모나 가족들은 산후보약 먹는 시기에 대해서 고민합니다 </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">산후보약이 필요하다는 것을 알면서도 출산 후 바로 보약을 먹으면 </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">혹시 몸에 문제가 생기지 않을까 걱정도 하게 됩니다</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><!-- Not Allowed Attribute Filtered ( onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6F5CA7C')\") --><img width=\"529\" height=\"373\" class=\"_photoImage\" id=\"20130902_89/isuhani_1378086828333gw6cd_PNG/%BB%EA%C8%C4%BA%B8%BE%E01.PNG\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 373px; rwidth: 529px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130902_89/isuhani_1378086828333gw6cd_PNG/%BB%EA%C8%C4%BA%B8%BE%E01.PNG?type=w3\" /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">산후보약은 출산으로 인해 생긴 어혈을 풀고 </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">산모의 기혈순환을 돕고 기력을 회복시키는 치료한약입니다 </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">처방은 산모의 건강상태나 체질 등을 고려하여 하게되며 소화하는데 지장을 주거나 </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">몸에 무리를 주는 치료가 이니기 때문에 음식이 섭취가능할 때 시작하시는 것이 좋습니다</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">오히려 출산 후 제대로 산후조리를 하지 않거나 </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">충분한 휴식기간 없이 일상으로 복귀하면 각종 문제가 찾아오기 쉽습니다 </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">대표적으로 산후비만, 산후우울증, 산후풍 등이 있으며 </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">오늘은 이러한 질환에 대해 산후보약잘짓는한의원에서 알아볼까 합니다</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><!-- Not Allowed Attribute Filtered ( onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6F5CA7C')\") --><img width=\"550\" height=\"302\" class=\"_photoImage\" id=\"20130902_264/isuhani_1378086870273ppBuI_PNG/%BB%EA%C8%C4%BA%B8%BE%E02.PNG\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 326px; rwidth: 592px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130902_264/isuhani_1378086870273ppBuI_PNG/%BB%EA%C8%C4%BA%B8%BE%E02.PNG?type=w3\" /></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">1.&nbsp; 산후비만</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 출산 과정에서 산모는 많은 에너지를 소비하기 때문에 충분한 영양섭취를 하게됩니다 </span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;반면 운동량은 줄어들기 때문에 이 과정에서 체중이 급격히 증가하게 되고&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 출산 후 식단관리와 운동을 통해 기존의 몸 상태로 돌아가는 경우도 있지만</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 출산 과정에서 소화기능에 문제가 생기고 몸 속에 독소가 쌓인 경우는 </span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 비만이 되기 쉽습니다</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 따라서 소화기능 회복과 몸안 독소 배출을 돕는 산후보약 치료가 필요합니다</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><!-- Not Allowed Attribute Filtered ( onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6F5CA7C')\") --><img width=\"392\" height=\"265\" class=\"_photoImage\" id=\"20130902_118/isuhani_1378086900882INV4K_PNG/%BA%F1%B8%B82.PNG\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 265px; rwidth: 392px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130902_118/isuhani_1378086900882INV4K_PNG/%BA%F1%B8%B82.PNG?type=w3\" /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">2. 산후풍</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 출산을 하게 되면 많은 출혈이 일어나고 통증이 산모에게 찾아옵니다 </span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 따라서 출산 후 충분한 회복과 관리가 필요한데 이를 소홀이 하면 몸에 찬기운이 들어와 </span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 비뇨생식기 기능저하 및 각종 통증을 일으키는 산후풍이 나타납니다</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><!-- Not Allowed Attribute Filtered ( onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6F5CA7C')\") --><img width=\"550\" height=\"193\" class=\"_photoImage\" id=\"20130902_160/isuhani_1378087104661RBNhB_PNG/%BE%EE%B1%FA2.PNG\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 260px; rwidth: 740px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130902_160/isuhani_1378087104661RBNhB_PNG/%BE%EE%B1%FA2.PNG?type=w3\" /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\"></span>&nbsp;</p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;산후풍은 일시적인 증상이 아니라 나이가 들면서 더욱 악화되기 쉽고 </span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 검사상 아무런 문제 발견되지 않는 경우가 많습니다</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 갑자기 무기력증이나 심리적 불안감이 찾아오고 식은땀이 나기도 합니다 </span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 따라서 산후보약 치료로 기력을 회복하고 뭉친 어혈을 풀어 </span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 제 기능을 할 수 있게 돕는 과정이 필요합니다</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">3. 산후 우울증</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140422_251/isuhani_13981263933259BBCS_JPEG/imagesCA3L4540.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"218\" height=\"231\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 231px; rwidth: 218px;\" id=\"20140422_251/isuhani_13981263933259BBCS_JPEG/imagesCA3L4540.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7CD8749')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140422_251/isuhani_13981263933259BBCS_JPEG/imagesCA3L4540.jpg?type=w3\"></span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 출산 후 급격한 심리변화로 우울감, 의욕상실, 두려움 등이 찾아오고 </span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 심각한 경우 자살충동까지 발생합니다 </span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 따라서 마음을 안정시키고 몸의 회복을 돕는 산후보약 치료와 함께 </span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 배우자나 가족의 따뜻한 관심이 필요합니다</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">산후의 다양한 질환에 고운맘카드를 사용할 수 있습니다. </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">경희 이수한의원&#8203;은 고운맘카드 지정한의원이기 때문에 사용이 가능합니다. </span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" />&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140422_78/isuhani_1398126393135NUs6D_PNG/%B0%ED%BF%EE%B8%BE%C4%AB%B5%E5.png?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"766\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 766px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20140422_78/isuhani_1398126393135NUs6D_PNG/%B0%ED%BF%EE%B8%BE%C4%AB%B5%E5.png\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7CD8749')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140422_78/isuhani_1398126393135NUs6D_PNG/%B0%ED%BF%EE%B8%BE%C4%AB%B5%E5.png?type=w3\"></span></span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&#8203;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 158, 37); font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&lt;&lt;산후보약/산후보약잘짓는한의원 진료시간안내&gt;&gt;</span></strong></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><!-- Not Allowed Attribute Filtered ( onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6F5CA7C')\") --><img width=\"545\" height=\"171\" class=\"_photoImage\" id=\"20130902_72/isuhani_1378087174784I4olY_PNG/%C1%F8%B7%E1%BD%C3%B0%A3.PNG\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 171px; rwidth: 545px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130902_72/isuhani_1378087174784I4olY_PNG/%C1%F8%B7%E1%BD%C3%B0%A3.PNG?type=w3\" /></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,dotum;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140422_106/isuhani_1398126433285hdfIn_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.j